@MemStack_HostAddress = http://localhost:5294

### 1. List all feature memories
GET {{MemStack_HostAddress}}/api/feature-memories
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get one by ID
GET {{MemStack_HostAddress}}/api/feature-memories/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Create a feature memory (POST)
POST {{MemStack_HostAddress}}/api/feature-memories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalFeatureId": "feature/promotion-engine-v2",
  "sourceSystem": "nexwork",
  "title": "Promotion Engine V2",
  "productName": "Coloris",
  "customerName": "Internal",
  "requirementMarkdown": "# Requirement\nBuild v2 of the promotion engine.",
  "implementationMarkdown": "# Implementation\nTBD",
  "summaryMarkdown": "# Summary\nTBD",
  "status": "Planned",
  "tags": "promotion,checkout"
}

###

### 4. Full update (PUT) - replaces all fields
PUT {{MemStack_HostAddress}}/api/feature-memories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalFeatureId": "feature/promotion-engine-v2",
  "sourceSystem": "nexwork",
  "title": "Promotion Engine V2",
  "productName": "Coloris",
  "customerName": "Internal",
  "requirementMarkdown": "# Requirement\nBuild v2 of the promotion engine.",
  "implementationMarkdown": "# Implementation\nService + queue added.",
  "summaryMarkdown": "# Summary\nAsync flow implemented.",
  "status": "InProgress",
  "tags": "promotion,checkout,async"
}

###

### 5. Partial update (PATCH) - only send what changed
PATCH {{MemStack_HostAddress}}/api/feature-memories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Done",
  "implementationMarkdown": "# Implementation\nCompleted and deployed."
}

###

### 6. Sync summary - called by Nexwork when feature completes
POST {{MemStack_HostAddress}}/api/feature-memories/1/sync-summary
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "summaryMarkdown": "# Summary\nPromotion engine v2 shipped successfully."
}

###

### 7. Delete
DELETE {{MemStack_HostAddress}}/api/feature-memories/1

###
